6. Harmony Check (Governance Layer Upgrade)

def check_harmony(state, action):
    return all([
        aligns_with_mission(action),
        respects_constraints(action),
        maintains_reversibility(action),
        coherence_score(action, state) > threshold
    ])

If false → dissonance → reject or recompose.

